title: Supercars.Exposed-Speed2008-Denver-PorscheSchool-CarreraGT
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Tanner visits Colorado to attend Porsche&#039;s Winter Driving School, featuring a lot of 911 models.  He also goes to a exotic car dealer in Denver to try and sell a Porsche Carrera GT.  Back in California, he gets to drive a Carrera GT flat out on a closed Malibu canyon road.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.  More episodes to come from tallearthling.
